description: This file defines the interface for managing GRE (Generic Routing Encapsulation) interface configurations in the COSA Data Model. It includes function prototypes for retrieving and setting interface parameters, counting entries, validation, commit, and rollback operations, all related to GRE interfaces.
external_methods: cosa_apis.h: API related to generic COSA data model functions

methods.name: GreIf_GetEntryCount
methods.description: Returns the count of GRE interface entries.

methods.name: GreIf_GetEntry
methods.description: Retrieves a specific GRE interface entry by index.

methods.name: GreIf_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Gets the boolean value of a specified parameter for a GRE interface.

methods.name: GreIf_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Gets the unsigned long value of a specified parameter.

methods.name: GreIf_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Gets the string value of a specified parameter.

methods.name: GreIf_GetParamIntValue
methods.description: Gets the integer value of a specified parameter.

methods.name: GreIf_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets the boolean value of a specified parameter.

methods.name: GreIf_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Sets the unsigned long value of a specified parameter.

methods.name: GreIf_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets the string value of a specified parameter.

methods.name: GreIf_SetParamIntValue
methods.description: Sets the integer value of a specified parameter.

methods.name: GreIf_Validate
methods.description: Validates the current configuration parameters before commit.

methods.name: GreIf_Rollback
methods.description: Rolls back any uncommitted configuration changes.

methods.name: GreIfStat_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves statistical unsigned long parameter value.
